{"tid":1946620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"個防疫措施根本就係打壓遊行集會自由再強推二十三條","createTime":"2020-03-27T18:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T20:38:41.000Z","uid":152114,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c45771861cc6224855797ba7467e53838a9cd6a0","tid":1946620,"uid":152114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:00:31.000Z","msg":"政府深夜公布該12類豁免群組，包括：<br />\n<br />\n1. 乘搭交通工具<br />\n2. 執行政府職能<br />\n3. 履行法定責任<br />\n4. 在工作地點工作<br />\n5. 醫院或醫護服務<br />\n6. 同一住戶單位內生活的人<br />\n7. 司法機構進行法律程序<br />\n8. 立法會或區議會的程序<br />\n9. 喪禮、祭祀先人<br />\n10. 不多於20人的婚禮<br />\n11. 團體履行法定責任的會議<br />\n12. 健康衛生講座<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遊行集會唔豁免<br />\n4個人以上公眾地方就犯法姐係合法遊行集會都搞唔成<br />\n依個時候推23條再用之前啲聯署黎support<br />\n過23條唔係夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5aa0c79b175b8af54be7b06b04991d42a33647","tid":1946620,"uid":152114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:04:49.000Z","msg":"以前用非法集結拉<br />\n依家用依條罪拉入到嘅機會易好多"},{"pid":"8fb1dfb2ef63d7128a2526552ca3ade5722a8608","tid":1946620,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:04:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7dc023d9af482a5d269c38d86a1f996e1ff24f93","tid":1946620,"uid":202296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:06:18.000Z","msg":"立法會排隊投票呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3da767e0ba941e6557c4391423da164d6f00e39","tid":1946620,"uid":152114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dc023d9af482a5d269c38d86a1f996e1ff24f93","tid":1946620,"uid":202296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:06:18.000Z","msg":"立法會排隊投票呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:08:40.000Z","msg":"8. 立法會或區議會的程序"},{"pid":"3731f9f3952a87f0d90718cff605c6723c1fa9a7","tid":1946620,"uid":152114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27